{"tid":1275400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家對記者客氣啲","createTime":"2019-07-01T19:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T20:23:07.000Z","uid":137440,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"608b8d179be588d5563c242f6a81b38f73d6b94b","tid":1275400,"uid":137440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:38:35.000Z","msg":"發夢有去現場既都知佢哋咩gear都冇但頭先都行最前影相 又食催淚彈又捱胡椒噴霧 幫大家爭取時間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反有義士下午做嘢既時候遮佢哋鏡頭就顯得有少少粗暴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遮鏡頭唔係問題<br />\n發夢我都會咁做<br />\n但希望大家可以客氣少少<br />\n加句對唔住都唔係用你好多時間<br />\n<br />\n記者（唔包括CCTVB）永遠都係我哋抗爭者既朋友 對住朋友客氣啲都冇所謂 但對住敵人就記得一定要往死裹打"},{"pid":"09220987b59dd602796ce1d0b57f8ef06a975c98","tid":1275400,"uid":137440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:45:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94cb44bf7067b56980c54d2400fd8d3aae21a5ab","tid":1275400,"uid":137440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508fc2b07a68ef2d5a018f1bfb54693f114abc71","tid":1275400,"uid":198310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:19:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ccae102cd403eda72155fdef2929f64e389ae8b1","tid":1275400,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:23:07.000Z","msg":"立場哥哥都講左警察都唔敢用手擋鏡頭<br />\n你話唔小心用遮擋住就話姐"}]}